metadata.name: Masquerade
metadata.description:
Insects are masters of camouflage when they hunt down their preys or disguise themselves. The preys won't even notice the looming menace. Similarly to when death comes knocking on your door, you won't even realize that this could be your last moment.

" once you see it, you can't unsee it "




Dimension : 3536 × 5000 pxl.
